{"tid":2429460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生大三罷當日無牌管有無線電通訊器 認罪今判感化","createTime":"2021-03-02T10:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T12:27:58.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7798c232257739a3cd3e055a7b5989167dbd55","tid":2429460,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T10:13:02.000Z","msg":"16歲男學生於前年「大三罷」當天早上，在天后被警察截查，搜出噴漆、面罩、剪刀、無線電通訊器等物，結果被控一項無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪。學生早前認罪，主任裁判官錢禮今在觀塘法院判刑，接納感化官建議，判處學生接<span class=\"red\">受18個月感化令</span>，其間須聽從感化官指示工作、居住和參加活動。"},{"pid":"00f1cbb5bb33b2156ead72c69c9b7ee6034c3538","tid":2429460,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/NYA22LX2WNE5JLOOGN2BEZRON4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2FNYA22LX2WNE5JLOOGN2BEZRON4%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=a553e23d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2FNYA22LX2WNE5JLOOGN2BEZRON4%2F&h=e1447c8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/NYA22LX2WNE5JLOOGN2BEZRON4/</a>"},{"pid":"f629b6520ebfc59afd53813f7a408d2b05636919","tid":2429460,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T10:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c26bb73cf8fbdb8523df06c901d32335f2fb476","tid":2429460,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e496de5943e0144067525606b8811623a1299d1","tid":2429460,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces